# Scythe is distributed as a precompiled plugin in this project.
# Keep its runtime DLLs and module manifests in source control so teammates can load it.
!Plugins/Scythe/
!Plugins/Scythe/Binaries/
!Plugins/Scythe/Binaries/Win64/
!Plugins/Scythe/Binaries/Win64/UnrealEditor-*.dll
!Plugins/Scythe/Binaries/Win64/UnrealEditor*.modules
Plugins/Scythe/Binaries/Win64/*-Win64-DebugGame.dll
Plugins/Scythe/Binaries/Win64/*.pdb
